>SAX handlers</a></dt>

<dd>
<p>Allowing XML::Twig to work on top of any SAX parser</p>

<dt><a name='multiple'></a><a name="multiple_twigs_are_not_well_supported"
>multiple twigs are not well supported</a></dt>

<dd>
<p>A number of twig features are just global at the moment. These include the ID list and the &#34;tag pool&#34; (if you use <code>change_gi</code> then you change the tag for ALL twigs).</p>

<p>A future version will try to support this while trying not to be to hard on performance (at least when a single twig is used!).</p>
</dd>
